- Added aternity_mapping.csv lookup file defining Account name and ID mapping to Aternity URL
- Adjusted Lookup Setup instructions

1.0.1 - 2019-09-14
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Added README


1.0.0 - 2019-09-10
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initial upload to Splunk base. The Application works with data supplied by the IT Squared / Cloud-Native Integration for Riverbed APM

Features:
- 8 custom dashboards for vizualization and analytics of the ingested AppInternals data
- Drilldowns into AppInternals that preserve context, including time ranges and monitored objects
- 6 out of the box pre-built panels globally available for embedding into user dashboards
- Data normalization and enrichment for out of the box integration with Splunk ITSI Module for Application Performance Monitoring
